trans-unit.target: The <unmanagedCodeEntityReference>Get Table ACL</unmanagedCodeEntityReference> operation is available in version 2012-02-12 and later.

trans-unit.source: An <newTerm>access control list</newTerm> (ACL) is a list of <newTerm>access control entries</newTerm> (ACE).
trans-unit.target: An <newTerm>access control list</newTerm> (ACL) is a list of <newTerm>access control entries</newTerm> (ACE).

trans-unit.source: Each ACE in an ACL identifies a <newTerm>trustee</newTerm> and specifies the <newTerm>access rights</newTerm> allowed, denied, or audited for that trustee.
trans-unit.target: Each ACE in an ACL identifies a <newTerm>trustee</newTerm> and specifies the <newTerm>access rights</newTerm> allowed, denied, or audited for that trustee.
